  "detailed_description": "This game is based on the classic novel Journey to the West and constructs a wonderful fantasy world of Journey to the West.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSun Xiao'ai, a modern girl who yearns for adventure, crossed into the body of Sun Xiaokong in the fantasy world of Journey to the West by chance.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAlong the way, he subdued demons and demons, subdued teammates with different personalities such as Zhu Xiaojie, Sha Xiaojing, Xiao Bailong, and Xiao Longnu, and went to the West to explore ways to return to the real world.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThis journey has gone through various wonderful adventures, and a huge conspiracy has gradually surfaced.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe Four Heavenly Kings, both righteous and evil? Is there another mastermind behind the Bull Demon King? Can Journey to the West Return to Peace Again? Is Sun Xiaoai's journey accidental or fate?<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIt all depends on you to slowly explore and discover! Welcome to the magical fantasy world of Journey to the West!",
  "about_the_game": "This game is based on the classic novel Journey to the West and constructs a wonderful fantasy world of Journey to the West.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSun Xiao'ai, a modern girl who yearns for adventure, crossed into the body of Sun Xiaokong in the fantasy world of Journey to the West by chance.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAlong the way, he subdued demons and demons, subdued teammates with different personalities such as Zhu Xiaojie, Sha Xiaojing, Xiao Bailong, and Xiao Longnu, and went to the West to explore ways to return to the real world.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThis journey has gone through various wonderful adventures, and a huge conspiracy has gradually surfaced.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe Four Heavenly Kings, both righteous and evil? Is there another mastermind behind the Bull Demon King? Can Journey to the West Return to Peace Again? Is Sun Xiaoai's journey accidental or fate?<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIt all depends on you to slowly explore and discover! Welcome to the magical fantasy world of Journey to the West!",
